4/* A structure that possibly contains a pointer to an object of type ISL_TYPE.
5 * The pointer in "value" is only valid if "valid" is isl_bool_true.
6 * Otherwise, "value" is set to NULL.
7 */
8struct ISL_MAYBE(ISL_TYPE) {
9 isl_bool valid;
10 ISL_TYPE *value;
11};
